### SWIFT ###

# The build directory: the compiled library, the tool, the harness adapter, and the test binaries,
# together with the C object files of the sibling deon-c package, all built on demand by `make` and by
# the harness scripts.
/build/

# SwiftPM's own directory, should anyone run `swift build` — this package builds with `make`, not
# SwiftPM, because SwiftPM will not reach the sibling's sources outside the package root.
/.build/
Package.resolved

# Object files and debug bundles.
*.o
*.dSYM/
